text: == Events == * March 21 – Henry V becomes King of England. * Project of Annals of Joseon Dynasty began. * The University of St Andrews is chartered by papal bull. == Births == *February 21 – Louis, Duke of Savoy (died 1465) *November 19 – Frederick II, Elector of Brandenburg (died 1470) == Deaths == *March 20 – Henry IV of England (born 1367) *September 26 – Stephen III, Duke of Bavaria (born 1337) *October 6 – Dawit I of Ethiopia (born 1382)
